B.Ni=new A.K(B.a8,"Reported speech in aviation reports","Aviation incident and accident reports frequently quote what crew members or controllers **said** or **thought**. The grammar used to report these statements is called **indirect/reported speech**.\n\nExam questions often ask you to convert between direct and reported speech, or complete a reported speech sentence correctly.",null,null,null)
B.Ob=new A.K(B.eM,"Watch the tense shift",null,null,B.q8,null)
B.NT=new A.K(B.B,"Tense Backshift Rule",'When the reporting verb is **past** (said, told, reported), tenses shift back:\n\n| Direct | Reported |\n|---|---|\n| is/am/are | **was/were** |\n| was/were | **had been** |\n| will | **would** |\n| can | **could** |\n| must | **had to** |\n| has/have + V3 | **had** + V3 |\n\n"The system **is** malfunctioning." \u2192\nThe pilot said the system **was** malfunctioning.',null,null,null)
B.IG=new A.az("The captain reported that the hydraulic pressure had dropped below limits.","Kaptan, hidrolik bas\u0131nc\u0131n limitin alt\u0131na d\xfc\u015ft\xfc\u011f\xfcn\xfc bildirdi.","had dropped")
